# iCloud Drive collision-rename pattern: when iCloud detects two
# concurrent edits to the same file, it renames the loser to "<name> 2.<ext>".
# These dupes are never wanted in git. Pattern matches "<basename> 2.<ext>"
# (a literal " 2" before the extension).
* 2.*
* 2
*\ 2.*
*\ 2
